Package dprocess

Interface Summary
RemoteCallback This interface define the standard behavior of a call back for the DProcess application The only implementing class is used on termination of a remote process.
RemoteProcess This interface defines the functionalities available on a remote process.
 

Class Summary
DPMessage This class defines a message format for the communication between the client and the server Used only in the context of a remote process creation.
